│    - `functions.initiate_payment`: Initiates payments between accounts.      │
│    - `functions.get_payment_status`: Checks payment statuses.                │
│    - `functions.cancel_payment`: Cancels pending payments.                   │
│    - `functions.send_alert`: Sends notifications to customers.               │
│    - `functions.get_notification_history`: Retrieves notification history.   │
│    - `functions.send_otp`: Sends one-time passwords for verification.        │
