│    - `functions.get_card_transactions`: Retrieves card transaction history.  │
│    - `functions.freeze_card`: Freezes customer cards.                        │
│    - `functions.unfreeze_card`: Unfreezes customer cards.                    │
│ 3. **Multi-tool Execution**:                                                 │
│    - `multi_tool_use.parallel`: Executes multiple tools simultaneously for   │
│ efficiency.                                                                  │
│                                                                              │
